{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-empty-line-before/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-colon-space-after/","description":"declaration-colon-space-before Require a single space or disallow whitespace before the colon of declarations. Options string:…","title":"declaration-colon-space-before"},"body":"<h1 id=\"declaration-colon-space-before\"><a href=\"#declaration-colon-space-before\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>declaration-colon-space-before</h1>\n<p>Require a single space or disallow whitespace before the colon of declarations.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color </span>:pink }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**       ↑\n * The space before this colon */</span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Options</h2>\n<p><code>string</code>: <code>\"always\"|\"never\"</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"always\"><a href=\"#always\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"always\"</code></h3>\n<p>There <em>must always</em> be a single space before the colon.</p>\n<p>The following patterns are considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>:pink }</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color </span>: pink }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color </span>:pink }</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"never\"><a href=\"#never\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"never\"</code></h3>\n<p>There <em>must never</em> be whitespace before the colon.</p>\n<p>The following patterns are considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color </span>: pink }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color </span>:pink }</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>:pink }</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/declaration-colon-space-before.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-colon-space-before/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-colon-space-before/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/declaration-colon-space-before/index.html.f2e65672a68d6c0e5f8577a607de7e7b.json"}